## Plot

Plot関数で取得したデータのグラフを作成することが可能




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(SONY$'6758.T.Adjusted')
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](quantmod_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-3-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::




また、専用のchartSeries関数やaddMACD関数でグラフを表示することも可能




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
chartSeries(SONY)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](quantmod_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=672}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
chartSeries(N225, theme = "white", subset='last 4 months')
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](quantmod_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-2.png){width=672}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
addMACD()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](quantmod_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-3.png){width=672}
:::
